Program: Discovery
Title: TRACE - Chasing the Sun
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrx3t
Last Broadcast Date: 02 April 1998
A new US solar observing satellite which will explore the Sun's outer rim. The TRACE project will look at the Sun's corona using high resolution images. Also in the programme, a vaccine against malaria and the so-called God particle. Presenter: Graham Easton.